OL,4,C'luring' pensioner to his death
OL,6,FA woman and a teenage boy have been
OL,7,Fjailed for murder after "luring" a
OL,8,Fpensioner to his death in Coventry.
OL,10,FMichael Brady was brutally killed
OL,11,Fbefore being shoved into an empty TV
OL,12,Fbox at a flat in Keresley.
OL,14,FAntoinette Sheppard and Kieron Spicer
OL,15,Fmurdered Mr Brady in a house on
OL,16,FBowness Close. They were both
OL,17,Fconvicted of his murder on 19 December
OL,18,F2023.
