OL,6,FSpicer's name was allowed to be
OL,7,Fpublished by the judge at sentencing,
OL,8,Fafter a prosecution application.
OL,10,Fsaid that Sheppard, 44, befriended her
OL,11,Fvictim Mr Brady, who was 74 at the
OL,12,Ftime of his death, and lured him to
OL,13,Fher home.
OL,15,FCCTV showed the victim entering her
OL,16,Faddress shortly after 6pm on June 18,
OL,17,F2023.
