OL,3,CTeenage boy and woman sentenced after
OL,4,C'luring' pensioner to his death
OL,6,FWatch the CCTV footage capturing the
OL,7,Fpair luring Mr Brady into the flat -
OL,8,Fand using his bank card to buy alcohol
OL,9,Fin a nearby shop after they murdered
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,FAt the same time, messages were
OL,13,Fexchanged between both killers as they
OL,14,Fdiscussed robbing Mr Brady - police
OL,15,Fbelieve it was around this time they
OL,16,Fmurdered the pensioner.
OL,18,FAfter killing Mr Brady, the pair put
OL,19,Fhis body in a large TV box, and
OL,20,Fdragged it into a shed to hide, the
OL,21,Fcourt heard.
