OL,6,FSheppard and Spicer then stole their
OL,7,Fvictim's bank card, withdrawing more
OL,8,Fthan #300 to buy alcohol, West
OL,9,FMidlands Police stated.
OL,11,FMembers of the public raised concerns,
OL,12,Fleading to police being called to the
OL,13,Faddress in Keresley. They searched the
OL,14,Fshed, discovering the body of Mr Brady.
OL,16,FDuring police interviews, both
OL,17,Fmurderers blamed each other for the
OL,18,Fdeath of Mr Brady. Jurors were shown
OL,19,Fphone messages in which Sheppard and
OL,20,FSpicer discussed inflicting violence
OL,21,Fon someone.
