OL,6,FOne from the teenager read: "I am on
OL,7,Fone. I am going to hurt people.'"
OL,9,FPolice say the now 17-year-old phoned
OL,10,FSheppard at this time and, when
OL,11,Fofficers answered, said: "If you want
OL,12,Fto speak to me, you will have to find
OL,13,Fme."
OL,15,FSpicer was later found after he told a
OL,16,Fsocial worker he had been asked to
OL,17,Fhide a body, a court heard.
