OL,4,C'luring' pensioner to his death
OL,6,FThe court heard how Sheppard had
OL,7,Fgroomed Spicer to commit offences and
OL,8,Fhow neither defendant showed any
OL,9,Fremorse.
OL,11,FSheppard has been jailed for a minimum
OL,12,Fof 30 years behind bars while Spicer
OL,13,Fwas sentenced to 18 years.
OL,15,FA victim statement from Mr Brady's
OL,16,Ffamily said: "We do not understand;
OL,17,Fnor will we ever understand the
OL,18,Fviolence shown to my dad, a
OL,19,Fvulnerable, ailing, gentle man who
OL,20,Ftrusted people.
