OL,3,CTeenage boy and woman sentenced after
OL,4,C'luring' pensioner to his death
OL,6,F"It was a planned and pre-meditated
OL,7,Fact of violence, with messages
OL,8,Fexchanged between both defendants
OL,9,Fdiscussing what they were going to do.
OL,11,F"Not only did they murder Mr Brady,
OL,12,Fbut they were both perfectly content
OL,13,Fto try and blame each other for it.
OL,15,F"We hope his family will take some
OL,16,Fclosure from this and that justice has
OL,17,Fbeen done."
